        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Shark Sales Elimination Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill makes it illegal to possess, buy, or sell shark parts or any product containing shark parts.A person may possess a shark part that was lawfully taken consistent with a license or permit under certain circumstances.</p> <p> Penalties are imposed for violations under the Magnuson-Stevens Fishery Conservation and Management Act.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
